Set below two environment variables to run the app:

1. MYSQL_PASSWORD: Password for root user of mysql instance
2. APP_SECRET_KEY: Required for encrypting session data by Flask

To generate random secret key through python:

>>> import os
>>> os.urandom(24)
b'Fnf>aV\xab\xbf@\x9dSwe\x8eC\xbe6\x0b\x9c\x05.\xad\xf5y'

To avoid escape issues in shell variables, regenerate the key till there are no conflicting characters

To run the app:

$ python run.py
